OL,3,CAt least 50 people killed and 700,000
OL,4,Cdisplaced by monsoon floods in India
OL,6,FFlooding in India's northeastern Assam
OL,7,Fstate has killed at least 50 people
OL,8,Fand displaced 700,000 after days of
OL,9,Fheavy monsoon rain overflowed the
OL,10,FBrahmaputra River, officials have said.
OL,12,FThe river, one of Asia's largest,
OL,13,Foriginates in China's Tibet region and
OL,14,Fflows about 900 kilometres (560 miles)
OL,15,Fthrough Assam.
OL,17,FIt has flooded villages, sweeping away
OL,18,Fhomes and forcing nearly 300,000
OL,19,Fpeople into government-run relief
OL,20,Fcamps, officials said on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
