OL,3,CAt least 50 people killed and 700,000
OL,4,Cdisplaced by monsoon floods in India
OL,6,FAuthorities are providing food and
OL,7,Frelief supplies to flood victims,
OL,8,Fusing airdrops from helicopters, Assam
OL,9,FChief Minister Himanta Biswa Sarma
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FNearly 900 villages have been
OL,13,Fsubmerged, and more than 7,000 homes
OL,14,Fwere without electricity, he said.
OL,16,FPolice, disaster response teams and
OL,17,Flocal volunteers were working to
OL,18,Frescue stranded residents and deliver
OL,19,Fessential supplies to flood-hit
OL,20,Fcommunities, officials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
