OL,3,CAt least 50 people killed and 700,000
OL,4,Cdisplaced by monsoon floods in India
OL,6,FJatin Gogoi, a 52-year-old farmer from
OL,7,FNazira, said the rising waters swept
OL,8,Faway his bamboo-walled home and
OL,9,Fdestroyed his livelihood.
OL,11,F"I lost all my cattle. My five-member
OL,12,Ffamily and I have nowhere to go, so we
OL,13,Fare taking shelter in a relative's
OL,14,Fhome," he said over the phone.
OL,16,FFlooding on Thursday evening disrupted
OL,17,Fparts of Guwahati, Assam's capital
OL,18,Fwith about two million residents, as
OL,19,Fsubmerged roads left commuters
OL,20,Fstranded for hours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
