OL,3,CAt least 50 people killed and 700,000
OL,4,Cdisplaced by monsoon floods in India
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"I had to stay overnight at my office.
OL,12,FThe roads were filled with water, some
OL,13,Fwaist deep," said Sudip Mazumdar, a
OL,14,Fjournalist in Guwahati.
OL,16,FExperts say human-caused climate
OL,17,Fchange is intensifying South Asia's
OL,18,Fmonsoons, which traditionally run from
OL,19,FJune to September and again from
OL,20,FOctober to December.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
