OL,3,CAt least 50 people killed and 700,000
OL,4,Cdisplaced by monsoon floods in India
OL,6,FThe rains, once predictable, now
OL,7,Farrive in erratic bursts that dump
OL,8,Fextreme amounts of water in short
OL,9,Fperiods, followed by dry spells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
